# Allowlist build context: the image needs reference/ and one spec file, nothing
# else. Everything not re-included below never reaches the Docker daemon, so an
# adopter vault, .git/, or any local file inside the clone cannot leak into a
# build even if it exists here.
*
!reference
!spec/wrap-tail-repair.example.yaml

# Belt and braces: even inside the re-included tree, never ship a vault or a
# local compose override (later lines win).
reference/docker/my-vault
reference/docker/docker-compose.yml
reference/docker/docker-compose.override.yml
**/.git
